text:
4th Avenue, west side, south from 39th Street. Extending from 40th to 41st Streets is Public School No. 136. At 42nd Street is St. Michaels Roman Catholic Church.

September 8, 1940

P. L. Sperr

39th Street, west from near Fourth Avenue toward the upper New York Bay. On Third Avenue is the B. M. T. elevated structure. The street-car tracks lead to the ferry which operates from the foot of 39th Street to St. George, Staten Island.

September 8, 1940

P. L. Sperr
